quran[7{c,v,t}:
63,5,aur jab un se kaha jaye ke aao rasool khuda tumahray liye mughfirat mangeen to sir hila dete hain aur tum un ko dekho ke taqqabur karte hue munh phair letay hain
63,6,tum un ke liye mughfirat mango ya nah mango un ke haq mein barabar hai. khuda un ko hargiz nah bakhshay ga. be shak khuda na farmanoon ko hadaayat nahi diya karta
63,7,yahi hain jo kehte hain ke jo log rasool khuda ke paas ( rehtay ) hain un par ( kuch ) kharch nah karo. yahan taq ke yeh ( khud bakhud ) bhaag jayen. halaank asmano aur zameen ke khazanay khuda hi ke hain lekin munhafiq nahi samajte
63,8,kehte hain ke agar hum lout kar madeeney puhanche to izzat walay zaleel logon ko wahan se nikaal bahar karen ge. halaank izzat khuda ki hai aur is ke rasool ki aur mominoun ki lekin munhafiq nahi jantay
63,9,momino! tumhara maal aur aulaad tum ko khuda ki yaad se ghaafil nah kardey. aur jo aisa kere ga to woh log khasara uthany walay hain
63,10,aur jo ( maal ) hum ne tum ko diya hai is mein se is ( waqt ) se peshtar kharch karlo ke tum mein se kisi ki mout aajay to ( is waqt ) kehnay lagey ke ae mere perwar-digaar to ne mujhe thori si aur mohlat kyun nah di taakay mein khairaat karleta aur naik logon mein daakhil hojata
63,11,aur jab kisi ki mout ajati hai to khuda is ko hargiz mohlat nahi deta aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is se khabardaar hai
